OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying very
OL,6,Fwarm into the evening with some late
OL,7,Fsunshine. A very warm and muggy night
OL,8,Fto follow, perhaps with a few mist and
OL,9,Ffog patches.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FVery hot and humid with
OL,12,Fstrong sunshine through the day. Light
OL,13,Fwinds and continuing to feel very warm
OL,14,Fand muggy into the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
